text: Ákos Gacsal (born 19 January 1994) is a Hungarian-born Slovak sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:People from Komárno Category:Slovak male canoeists Category:Canoeists at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Slovakia
